Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.88,0:22:03.30,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}純真さが シンプルな力に 変わる 世界に影をつくりだす
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.95,0:22:17.84,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}ガラスケ一スに横たわる 光の存在に触れたくても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.92,0:22:24.94,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}振り上げた手 降ろせなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.31,0:22:33.61,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}落ちるようにしゃがみこんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.74,0:22:41.93,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}Prototype boy 明日の理想だけで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.17,0:22:49.42,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}語り継ぐような 美談にもならないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.63,0:22:56.75,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}この体を失いそうな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.95,0:23:05.92,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}ギリギリの場所が 哀しいくらい似合ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.88,0:22:03.30,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}当纯真变为单纯的力量 世界由此诞生了影子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.95,0:22:17.84,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}穿透过玻璃橱 感触着这光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.92,0:22:24.94,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}举起的手无法放下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.31,0:22:33.61,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}却如同坠落般跌下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.74,0:22:41.93,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}Prototype boy 抛开明天的理想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.17,0:22:49.42,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}即便无法成为传承的美谈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.63,0:22:56.75,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}如同就要失去这副身躯一般
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.95,0:23:05.92,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}在极限的边缘 跌入悲伤的深渊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.55,0:00:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关押反政府势力人员的设施遭到Gundam的袭击是毋庸置疑的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.08,0:00:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是天行者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.59,0:00:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传言说反政府势力独立开发了Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.64,0:00:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个还只是猜测
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.51,0:00:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论怎么说 这都是威胁现政府的恐怖活动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.56,0:00:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政府为了剿灭恐怖组织
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.88,0:00:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定派遣直属治安维持部队
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.14,0:00:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预见了天行者的复活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.15,0:00:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并借此机会扩大A-LAWS的权限么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.37,0:00:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的主意..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.51,0:00:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是维塔的主意？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.37,0:00:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.77,0:00:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 差不多该我们出场了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.60,0:00:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里瓦夫·里巴尔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.98,0:00:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加德萨机型已经下线了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.10,0:00:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有命令 随时都可以出击
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.56,0:00:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还没有这个必要 里瓦夫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.86,0:01:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个作战 已经拜托某人了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.17,0:01:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某人？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.24,0:01:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪瓦恩？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.47,0:01:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是布林格?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.56,0:01:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个人类
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.43,0:01:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然从某个角度来说 已经不属于人类了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.04,0:02:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆在家太无聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.46,0:02:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.96,0:03:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ptolemaios的修理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.64,0:03:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS的新型MS的调查
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.12,0:03:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00的TWIN DRIVE系统的调整
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.28,0:03:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做的事还有很多哟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.59,0:03:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的啦 不过还是不爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.93,0:03:16.38,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁布哈利沙漠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.79,0:03:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种地方… 竟然没被联邦发现
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.13,0:03:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦在非加盟国很多的中东全域撒布GN粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听他们说建造的目的是用粒子效果来干扰恐怖组织的联络网
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.10,0:03:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过实际上却是为了妨碍中东的经济活动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.57,0:03:39.10,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN粒子散布装置
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.41,0:03:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让不遵从联邦意志的国家尝尝苦头
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.94,0:03:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过也算托了GN粒子的福 KATARON的设施没有被发现
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.29,0:03:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解的真清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.92,0:03:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？只是常识啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.86,0:03:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了吗 已确认到你们的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.49,0:03:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在打开舱门
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.64,0:03:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.41,0:04:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.65,0:04:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救了阿扎帝斯坦的英雄机体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们来了真是太好了 天行者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.57,0:04:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎你们到来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看看你们的相貌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.67,0:04:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.63,0:04:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有保密义务
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.46,0:04:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么不通情理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.79,0:04:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家是拔刀相助的朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.90,0:04:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反政府组织KATARON
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.30,0:04:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢你们能与我们会谈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.16,0:04:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是KATARON中东支部的克劳斯·古拉德
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.86,0:04:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是天行者 自我介绍的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.05,0:04:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 我理解你们的难处
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢你们帮助了玛丽娜公主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.61,0:04:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后我们将尽到保护她的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.30,0:04:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诗琳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.46,0:04:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想呆在天行者那边吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.41,0:04:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是 竟然加入反政府组织
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.10,0:05:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.82,0:05:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一个人想托你们保护
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈·库洛斯洛特 平民
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.65,0:05:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说 他因为被A-LAWS怀疑是KATARON的成员才牵扯进来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.97,0:05:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可真该说声抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.12,0:05:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会负起责任保护你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.66,0:05:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 这样擅做主张…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.31,0:05:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是做好的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.84,0:05:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.51,0:05:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要随意跑进来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.55,0:05:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.16,0:05:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.87,0:05:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算培养他们成为KATARON的成员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.47,0:05:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别误会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.08,0:05:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是保护这些没有安身之所的孩子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.39,0:05:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦施行的片面的中东政策
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.78,0:05:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其危害就以这种形式表现出来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.24,0:06:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来因为资金所限 不能接收全部的孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.91,0:06:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是玛丽娜大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.49,0:06:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是 玛丽娜·伊斯玛依露大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.42,0:06:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.92,0:06:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.70,0:06:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了 真的是玛丽娜大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.35,0:06:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽娜大人 能陪孩子玩一会吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.47,0:06:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.26,0:06:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗？那么我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去 我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.96,0:06:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是王国的象征啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.97,0:06:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该进入正题了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.71,0:06:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们KATARON是为了打倒现联邦政权…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉 我们并不是像你们一样按政治的思想行动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.86,0:06:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你们也和联邦是对立的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.27,0:06:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的敌人不是联邦政府 而是A-LAWS
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.37,0:06:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和政府直属的部队战斗的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.26,0:06:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那和我们的目的不是一致的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.55,0:06:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样 为了制止A-LAWS的恶行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.11,0:06:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要联手合作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.11,0:07:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾 这里的MS是不能和搭载GN DRIVE的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.10,0:07:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此 我们也想帮助你们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是补给还是整备
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都想助你们一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.60,0:07:14.38,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波斯湾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.45,0:07:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Trilobite的损失 真是失态啊 少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉 给部队丢脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.61,0:07:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛奈金大佐 和少佐一起担任部队的指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.30,0:07:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.70,0:07:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们A-LAWS是联邦的矛和盾 不允许失败
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.08,0:07:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样 今后要听从我的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.13,0:07:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗 Mr.武士道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.55,0:07:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恕我断然拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.40,0:07:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.38,0:07:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从司令部获得了独自行动的许可
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.01,0:07:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是one man army 只有一个人的军队
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.32,0:07:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种任性的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.87,0:07:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过有许可了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.17,0:08:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐出动了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.76,0:08:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我负责Gundam的搜索部队
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.59,0:08:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是作为正规军给A-LAWS当打杂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.63,0:08:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.15,0:08:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 那家伙还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.12,0:08:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是说安德雷少尉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.74,0:08:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忠实的完成着任务
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.90,0:08:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是做给我看的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.73,0:08:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙恨我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.65,0:08:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我只做了军人 而不是一名父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.96,0:08:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.63,0:08:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐 那件事…我想可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.14,0:08:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪件事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.47,0:08:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当大佐的养女那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.58,0:08:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.08,0:08:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,详细的等见面再说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.79,0:08:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.06,0:08:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是幸运的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.53,0:09:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽娜大人 这个 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.59,0:09:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.48,0:09:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不到这边来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.01,0:09:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.95,0:09:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些孩子也是你们的受害者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.03,0:09:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你们妄图改变世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.63,0:09:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.78,0:09:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么也感受不到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.52,0:09:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会感受不到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.19,0:09:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不可能再次踏入那里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.18,0:09:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你明白 为什么还要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.82,0:10:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有这样做的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.17,0:10:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不指望你能了解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.02,0:10:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使你恨我也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.87,0:10:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.75,0:10:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.01,0:10:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走了么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.24,0:10:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前 希望你能接受我一个请求
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.00,0:10:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想同天行者联合 果然还是不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.71,0:10:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那个回答已经足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.64,0:10:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和A-LAWS的战斗一定会非常激烈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.00,0:10:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不远的将来 他们与我们联手的日子一定会到来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.38,0:10:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说是吧 G1
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.59,0:10:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.69,0:10:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你们要偷懒到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.20,0:10:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快回岗位干活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.53,0:10:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会谈结束了么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.08,0:10:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 但是还有一件事要做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.99,0:10:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.21,0:10:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把玛丽娜·伊斯玛依露送到阿扎帝斯坦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.55,0:11:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.14,0:11:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.25,0:11:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉 提出无理的请求
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.78,0:11:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能使用Gundam哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.90,0:11:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一被发现了 可能会危害到阿扎帝斯坦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.09,0:11:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我使用这个机体
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.49,0:11:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把Gundam送回托勒密
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.86,0:11:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.22,0:11:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 你不回来也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.58,0:11:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说胡话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.07,0:11:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这四年间发生什么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.79,0:11:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以前不开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.28,0:11:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.60,0:11:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.33,0:11:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是天行者还是KATARON
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.51,0:11:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是些挑起战争的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.06,0:11:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能呆在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.47,0:11:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.88,0:11:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是天行者的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.22,0:12:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城镇里有个朋友 我想联络他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.18,0:12:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城镇还远呢 开车去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.72,0:12:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.97,0:12:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有看到玛丽娜公主
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.73,0:12:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才还和天行者一伙在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.82,0:12:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他们在一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.28,0:12:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam要返回母舰了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请打开升降口
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.83,0:12:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.21,0:12:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止出发
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.74,0:12:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽娜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.36,0:12:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这玩意能穿越沙漠吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.55,0:12:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦军
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.45,0:13:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那么点准备 为什么还在沙漠里跑!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.20,0:13:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生物检测结果出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.04,0:13:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是KATARON的成员
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.21,0:13:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不! 我才不是的!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.94,0:13:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还撒谎!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.25,0:13:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别给我动粗!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.79,0:13:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大…大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.44,0:13:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.62,0:13:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来的话我来问
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.08,0:13:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是战士吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.48,0:13:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在军队呆久了所以看得出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.70,0:13:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的目光里并没有战斗者的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.34,0:13:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 并不是KATARON的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.53,0:13:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底 都发生过什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.64,0:13:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和天行者组织一同行动过的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.76,0:13:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说是有理由的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.36,0:13:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看资料的话 你在数周之前Gundam出现的PLANT上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.05,0:13:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从事殖民卫星开发的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.88,0:14:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后现在你出现在 昨天同Gundam战斗过的这片区域里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.55,0:14:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 简单的推理而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.45,0:14:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.06,0:14:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既不是KATARON也不是天行者的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.89,0:14:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.02,0:14:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想听你把经过讲一讲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.53,0:14:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会伤害你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.88,0:14:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够洗清我身上的嫌疑么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.93,0:14:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会尽力的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.59,0:14:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四宇宙舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.81,0:14:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴拉克·齐宁大尉同属下5人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在抵达
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.09,0:14:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.81,0:14:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么? 那是真的么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.14,0:14:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上送去指令书
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.92,0:14:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个天真的女人的话会坏了事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.87,0:14:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好消息 司令
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.66,0:14:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现了KATARON的军事基地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.35,0:14:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是很可能Gundam也在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.90,0:14:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上采取对应措施
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.63,0:14:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.51,0:14:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令 请也给我们出击许可
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.55,0:14:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别硬来 先休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.29,0:15:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明Gundam也在的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.95,0:15:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这指令书是什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.65,0:15:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然要使用自走机械人的Kill-Mode?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.27,0:15:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.33,0:15:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,执行这种非人道的作战…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.86,0:15:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.07,0:15:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上层部的命令是绝对的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.74,0:15:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份作战的内容 阁下什么都感觉不到么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.47,0:15:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然感觉不到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.37,0:15:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方是反政府势力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.79,0:15:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有给予同情的必要哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.69,0:15:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要进行这种作战…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.25,0:15:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐反对转属到这里的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.03,0:15:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.61,0:15:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉误解了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.58,0:15:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米卢诺夫大佐这个人为了任务的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.23,0:15:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是连骨肉之亲都能够舍弃的男人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.73,0:15:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连骨肉之亲都…?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.28,0:15:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人眼睁睁看着母亲死去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.30,0:16:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.61,0:16:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS知道了反政府组织的位置…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.08,0:16:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.50,0:16:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这边来和提艾利亚进行联系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.12,0:16:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混账!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.76,0:16:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁说过让你报告给A-LAWS了!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那是我们的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.01,0:16:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做出判断的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.66,0:16:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库洛斯洛特君 现在马上从这里逃走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.97,0:16:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.30,0:16:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS得知了你的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.87,0:16:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙是在法律之上行动的部队
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.32,0:16:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我的权限保护不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.23,0:16:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.40,0:16:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快一点!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.14,0:16:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说我的存在被知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.31,0:16:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道… 嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.80,0:16:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种颜色…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.82,0:16:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从王留美发来的紧急加密通信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.76,0:16:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS的MS部队
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.55,0:16:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎正在向KATARON的设施进发
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.93,0:16:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去救援了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.46,0:17:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密 张开对卫星光学迷彩 紧急上浮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.25,0:17:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行Gundam的出击准备
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.74,0:17:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白的说!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.79,0:17:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密号 紧急上浮开始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.35,0:17:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离海面剩余时间0043
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.43,0:17:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被A-LAWS发现了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.33,0:17:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明那里还有小孩子在的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.86,0:17:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点 快点啊混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.14,0:17:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS的MS队来了!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.66,0:17:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是来摧毁这里的么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.67,0:17:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人的数量是!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从哪里得知基地的情报的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.89,0:17:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道 是天行者!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.22,0:17:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点吧孩子们带到掩体里!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.12,0:17:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好的!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.10,0:17:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳斯 出击吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.80,0:17:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战力差别太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.85,0:17:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加强防御 等待天行者的救援
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.05,0:17:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会来吗!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.22,0:17:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信他们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.44,0:17:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轰炸么?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.04,0:18:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,视线确认怀疑为敌方基地的建筑物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.88,0:18:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方MS出现!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.40,0:18:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用那种旧型的MS…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.92,0:18:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转入扫荡敌方基地的作战
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.45,0:18:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自走机械人 射出
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.86,0:18:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.68,0:18:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自走机械人 射出
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.72,0:18:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等一下!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.26,0:18:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.70,0:18:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军用自走机械人!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.26,0:18:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员 隐蔽!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.23,0:18:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.29,0:18:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迟了一步么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.56,0:18:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KATARON的人们呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.00,0:19:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里交给你们了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.08,0:19:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快一点 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.40,0:19:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮瑞斯机 去迎击先行的Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.09,0:19:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明…明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.31,0:19:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种动作!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.44,0:19:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各机 迎击Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.51,0:19:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先行告辞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.39,0:19:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr.武士道 为什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.49,0:19:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没兴趣!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.25,0:19:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.83,0:19:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是… 这他妈是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.43,0:19:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人做的事情么!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.63,0:19:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用无人兵器进行的虐杀行为
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.91,0:19:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然连扳机都不自己扣下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.86,0:19:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连罪恶感都不打算承担么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.16,0:20:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双射炮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.16,0:20:00.50,Second,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,1008)}Double Bazooka
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.19,0:20:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆发模式
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.19,0:20:02.71,Second,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,1008)}Burst Mode
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.87,0:20:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初期目标已经完成 撤退!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.44,0:20:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饶不了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.93,0:20:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我饶不了你们! A-LAWS!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.12,0:20:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.04,0:20:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别他妈给我逃啊 A-LAWS!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.01,0:20:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.63,0:20:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是… A-LAWS
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.60,0:20:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.75,0:20:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是 我们的死敌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.47,0:21:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是超兵 为了战斗的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.15,0:21:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的我却渴望得到正常人的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.90,0:21:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是那样做的惩罚么? 大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.15,0:21:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.99,0:21:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为我告诉了他们才…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.04,0:21:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.53,0:21:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.95,0:21:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.84,0:23:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上 就到阿扎帝斯坦了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.01,0:23:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够回来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.67,0:23:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 你的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.26,0:23:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿扎帝斯坦在…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.04,0:23:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃烧着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.16,0:23:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 阿扎帝斯坦会…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.21,0:23:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.90,0:23:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种规模 不是恐怖袭击什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.98,0:23:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.40,0:23:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 那个颜色是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.22,0:23:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.05,0:23:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.87,0:23:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你猜对了啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.11,0:24:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去不返的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.72,0:24:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去不返的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.27,0:24:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去不返的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.06,0:24:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无一不揪扯着什么人的心
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.81,0:24:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.86,0:24:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名为后悔的隐痛 阵阵袭来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.20,0:00:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.68,0:21:05.54,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prototype boy 明日の理想だけで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.94,0:21:16.10,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,語り継ぐような 美談にもならないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.16,0:21:25.86,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,この体を失いそうな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.29,0:21:38.29,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ギリギリの場所が 哀しいくらい似合ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.68,0:21:05.54,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prototype boy 抛开明天的理想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.94,0:21:16.10,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便无法成为传承的美谈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.16,0:21:25.86,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同就要失去这副身躯一般
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.29,0:21:38.29,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在极限的边缘 跌入悲伤的深渊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.29,0:21:40.29,EDcn,,0000,0000,0000,,

